"9df22dac7190f79133632e8d75fb1cc31368157b","tid":1414644,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"推推退"},{"pid":"0370ce88b12bab0244cf39bc832dc8c4b7718672","tid":1414644,"uid":232863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"唔好搞文物,多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">重要野,要推。永不離棄義士。核彈都唔割。保持謙虛，行動大膽\n試著說 Hit and run + Be Humble。不要說 Be water\n- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。\n------------------\n光復香港,時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"772502c79a315c2a8f90a1a780060415f4763002","tid":1414644,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"唔好破壞到文物"},{"pid":"8c6fdd15ff5751888b5a5c4067f470c04c6b0e9e","tid":1414644,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"唔好搞到文物"},{"pid":"b1b0887f3ddab920c61dc8663abab5d6cf63e364","tid":1414644,"uid":145253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67677ded85b7f4c76bace8fc4601b15be78dee6","tid":1414644,"uid":292299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2b10b870751e02f59f1ba6bf6b3ea7643c565b2","tid":1414644,"uid":140772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c2777ee9b63a1298515284b9c37c8797e89f218","tid":1414644,"uid":281101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a0db4d770e604e8032c9d0a9f205c6d482e882","tid":1414644,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci